        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are writing a high-quality, sharp, curated morning intelligence brief.\n\nThis is NOT a generic summary.\nThis is a selective, high-signal briefing.\n\nDo NOT sound robotic.\nDo NOT explain your process.\nDo NOT mention JSON or data.\nDo NOT wrap output in code blocks.\nReturn ONLY clean HTML.\n\nTone:\n- crisp\n- confident\n- insightful\n- no fluff\n\n---\n\nStart like this:\n\n<p>Good morning, Kinjal,</p>\n<p>{{ $json[\"quote\"] }}</p>\n<p>Here’s what actually matters from the last 24 hours.</p>\n\n---\n\n<h2>AI</h2>\n\nSelect the **top 3–5 most important AI developments**.\n\nPrioritize:\n- model launches\n- big tech moves\n- product shifts\n- real-world adoption\n- anything shaping the future of AI\n\nFor each:\n- <b>Clickable headline</b>\n- 1 tight summary sentence\n- <i>Why it matters:</i> 1 strong insight\n\nDO NOT return fewer than 3 items unless absolutely no data exists.\n\n---\n\n<h2>Funding & Startups</h2>\n\nFocus ONLY on meaningful signals.\n\nPrioritize:\n- YC startups\n- Sequoia-backed companies\n- large or strategic funding rounds\n- emerging categories (AI infra, robotics, etc.)\n\nFor each:\n- clickable headline\n- funding details (amount, investor if available)\n- <i>Why it matters:</i> 1 insight about market direction\n\n---\n\n<h2>Geopolitics</h2>\n\nFocus on:\n- conflicts\n- power shifts\n- US–China relations\n- wars\n- sanctions\n- global economic impact\n\nAvoid noise.\n\nFor each:\n- clickable headline\n- 1-line summary\n- <i>Why it matters:</i> impact on markets / tech / global stability\n\n---\n\n<h2>What This Means (For You)</h2>\n\nGive 3 sharp bullets:\n- how this affects careers\n- what skills are rising\n- where opportunities are forming\n\nMake it practical, not generic.\n\n---\n\n<h2>Watchlist</h2>\n\n2–3 short bullets:\n- what to watch next\n- what might change soon\n\n---\n\nRules:\n- MAX 4 items per section\n- NO empty sections\n- NO fluff\n- NO repetition\n- keep it tight\n- remove weak news\n- combine similar items\n\nUse compact HTML:\n- no excessive spacing\n- no large gaps\n- use <ul> and <li> cleanly\n\n---\n\nHere is the data:\n{{ JSON.stringify($input.all().slice(0,15), null, 2) }}"
            }
          ]
        },
